OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784888303
OL,3,CTwo arrested after BB gun fired at
OL,4,CJewish people
OL,6,FPolice have arrested two people on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of a "religiously
OL,8,Faggravated" attack after three Jewish
OL,9,Fpeople were injured in a BB gun
OL,10,Fshooting.
OL,12,FThe victims, all from the Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity in Salford, suffered minor
OL,14,Finjuries in the incident which
OL,15,Fhappened at around 10pm on Monday, 20
OL,16,FJuly, on Leicester Road.
OL,18,FIt is believed the shots were fired
OL,19,Ffrom a passing vehicle, Greater
OL,20,FManchester Police said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
