OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784888303
OL,3,CTwo arrested after BB gun fired at
OL,4,CJewish people
OL,6,FFollowing "extensive" CCTV enquiries,
OL,7,Fofficers arrested two suspects on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of religiously aggravated
OL,9,Fcommon assault.
OL,11,FIn statement, a spokesperson from the
OL,12,Fforce said: "Threats to our
OL,13,Fcommunities will not be tolerated and
OL,14,Fwe're continuing to enhance our
OL,15,Fsecurity in Jewish communities across
OL,16,FGreater Manchester to help keep them
OL,17,Fsafe on our streets."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
